responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "F895BF3A4478D64A3BEBDAB0ED1C8FB5", "P.14.Month and Day: The Order of Bloom have turned to we tradesmen for new fodder in their war against the Harrower\'s horde. We can no longer avoid this. I have volunteered to fight and Aly shall stay here to maintain the estate and watch over my beloved Isa. May the Seven Shine Upon Us!")
